hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw4.collections

Class SimpleHashtable

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw4.collections.SimpleHashtable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<SimpleHashtable.TableEntry>

    public class SimpleHashtable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<SimpleHashtable.TableEntry>
    This class is an implementation of hash map collection. It contains values which are mapped to distinct keys. Most of methods in this map implementation have complexity O(1). Any object can be assigned as key or value in this map, but keys must be distinct. This class implements IterableSimpleHashtable.TableEntry so it can be used in short version of for loop. With addition of more elements to the map, the capacity will change accordingly.
